<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>도서 신청 수정</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Prompt:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap');
        
        *{
            list-style: none;
        }

        .all {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        h1{
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 120px;
        }
        .sub {
            text-align: center;
            color: #9A9A9A;
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        a{
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }
        button{
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 17px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 6px 20px;
        }
        .submit{
            background-color: #8BD9B3;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            margin-top: 25px;
            font-family: 'Prompt', sans-serif;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-size: 500;
        }
        .cancel{
            background-color: #D1DED8;
            margin-top: 25px;
            margin-right: 5px;
            font-family: 'Prompt', sans-serif;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;

        }


        .form-font{
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 13px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        input{
            width: 245px;
            height: 34px;
            background-color: #e8e8e8;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding-left: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        .input-name{
            width: 245px;
            height: 30px;
            background-color: #e8e8e8;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding-left: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 2px;
            font-family: 'Prompt', sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            padding-top: 9px;
        }

        .logo-img{
            width: 80px;
            height: 90px
        }
        .btn-wrapper {
            display: flex;
             justify-content: flex-end;
        }
        .logout{
            font-family: 'Prompt', sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #8BD9B3;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
    

    <a href="/logout" class="logout">LOGOUT</a>
    <div class="all">
        <h1>도서 신청 수정</h1>
        <p class="sub"> 수정 하고 싶은 도서의 상세 정보를 작성해주세요.</p>
        <div class="input-style">
            <form action="/update/<%=book_re[0].id %>" method="post">
                <p class="form-font">신청자 (수정불가)</p> <input type="text" name="name" value="<%=book_re[0].name %>" readonly><br>
                <p class="form-font">도서 이름</p><input type="text" name="bookname" value="<%=book_re[0].bookname %>" required><br>
                <p class="form-font">출판사 </p><input type="text" name="publisher" value="<%=book_re[0].publisher%>"required><br>
                <p class="form-font">가격 </p> <input type="text" name="price" value="<%=book_re[0].price %>" required><br>
                <div class="btn-wrapper">
                    <button type="button" class="cancel" onclick="location.href='/list'">목 록</button> 
                    <button type="submit" class="submit">수 정</button>
                </form>   
                </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
    
    
        
</body>
</html>